DESCRIPTION:Renew Azure Trusted/Artifact Signing identity verification at au10tix before it expires.\n\nSteps:\n1. Log into Azure Portal (portal.azure.com)\n2. Navigate to: Artifact Signing → <your account> → Identity Validation\n3. Re-upload government-issued photo ID\n4. Take new selfie\n5. Re-scan Microsoft Authenticator QR code\n\nIf automated check passes: verification returns in HOURS.\nIf escalated: up to SEVERAL DAYS — do not wait until last minute.\n\nCanon ref: azure-signing-setup.md §6 · K-C BP058 W6
